	(text "The OV5640 internally generates 1.5V DVDD \nfrom AVDD (2.8V) using an onboard LDO\nIf the internal regulator is enabled, DVDD \nshould be left floating (not connected externally)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 258.826 128.27 0)
		(effects
